    "7411610": {
        "Desc": "Talk to everyone",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Boss",
                    "T": "Stop! I surrender! Ahaha... Well, what a coincidence! Are you here for the treasure, too?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Intrepid Valberry\"",
                    "T": "Why are you all here? Don't you believe me?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Valberry! We're here to look for Sir Arthur. Are you here for the treasure?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Intrepid Valberry\"",
                    "T": "Ha! I knew this dirty dog would come for the treasure if he heard about the news. And I got him!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rocher",
                    "T": "Um, agents... May I have the chest? I'm looking for Sir Arthur, and if I can return it to the newspaper, I might just be able to get a job..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rocher",
                    "T": "Then I can make some money and buy my wife's things back..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Intrepid Valberry\"",
                    "T": "Bah! How pathetic! Rocher, you really think that's why your wife left you, huh? She left because you're such a pushover!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Intrepid Valberry\"",
                    "T": "Stand up for yourself like you did just now, and she might look at you differently!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rocher",
                    "T": "R—Really?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Intrepid Valberry\"",
                    "T": "Of course! Now, be brave and let them have the treasure, or your wife won't be with you even in your next life!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rocher",
                    "T": "Don't... Don't say that!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kevin",
                    "T": "Take it easy. They're nice people! If you help them, they'll pay you back!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rocher",
                    "T": "In that case, thank you... and please, take these."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
