    "7411641": {
        "Desc": "Place Curve's core into the control panel",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Rocher",
                    "T": "It's... it's Sir Arthur's body! Ah! So... so cruel..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "And... is there anything else?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Then it should be in the final place."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kevin",
                    "T": "Baulande, come on, we're heading to the next place."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Baulande! Lombroso!",
                    "T": "Woof! Woof!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rocher",
                    "T": "Huh? Lombroso? Where did you run off to? I thought you didn't need me anymore..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Baulande! Lombroso!",
                    "T": "(The puppy wags its tail excitedly, as if saying, \"How's that possible?\")"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kevin",
                    "T": "Lombroso? Er, Mister Rocher, are you mistaken? His name is Baulande..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rocher",
                    "T": "What? If it wasn't for Lombroso's companionship, I wouldn't have made it this far. How could I be mistaken..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kevin",
                    "T": "Not like I can be mistaken either! What's going on here..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Intrepid Valberry\"",
                    "T": "Hey! Can't he belong to you both? Seeing as even I've had more than one home!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, that makes sense! Kevin accidentally drove the puppy away before, right? Maybe that's when he met Rocher and they began roaming around together..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rocher",
                    "T": "I—Is that really what happened?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Baulande! Lombroso!",
                    "T": "(The puppy wags its tail excitedly, as if saying, \"That's right!\")"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Boss",
                    "T": "Valberry! You've got some nerve! The dog wouldn't forget its two owners, and as for you, you betrayed your own boss twice!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Intrepid Valberry\"",
                    "T": "You scheming dog! I'm going to hand you over to the Marechaussee Phantom! I'm taking you down with me!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "\"Intrepid Valberry\"",
                    "T": "Ah, farewell, friends! Come visit me in the Fortress of Meropide someday!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Who the heck wants to go visit you there!? Well... never mind, forget about them. We need to hurry up and get to the last place."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, Kevin and Rocher! Are you going to fight for the puppy?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kevin",
                    "T": "No way! I was the one who really messed up. Baulande can stay wherever he wants from now on."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Rocher",
                    "T": "I... I'm fine with that too... Lombroso supported me when I was at my worst. I'll support him, too!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's get going then."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yes! We don't want anyone to beat us to it."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
