    "7411637": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Talochard",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Talochard",
                    "T": "Curve... you..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Talochard",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Just now..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Talochard",
                    "T": "NO! I need to go back and find Curve!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uh, uhm... Talochard... Don't be too reckless..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Going back is extremely dangerous."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah! There was just an explosion, and it's so deep underwater... Curve wouldn't want you running right back into danger!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Talochard",
                    "T": "You are... *sigh*... You are correct, I shouldn't act like this..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But... didn't he say the self-destruct mechanism could be shut off?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "He lied."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Talochard",
                    "T": "...He can't shut it down, his core can only open the emergency exit..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So then why..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Talochard",
                    "T": "His core had to be inside the control panel to open the emergency exit... But he's smart now, he knew we wouldn't leave him behind..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Talochard",
                    "T": "So he lied to us..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh wow... He can already think like that? Wouldn't that... when did he..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Talochard",
                    "T": "It must have been Dr. Mosso's letter that made Curve understand the final question... He learned about what Dr. Mosso did for him..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Talochard",
                    "T": "Turns out I'm useless after all... If only I were more competent, maybe I could have helped him break the protocols, and we wouldn't have had to come here..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "But the letter might just have been the final push."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That's right. Don't blame yourself, Curve's breakthrough probably started a long time ago..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Talochard",
                    "T": "His breakthrough... had already started?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Let's say you eat 100 Slimes in one sitting and get super fat! You can't blame it all on the last Slime."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "It's the same with Curve. Even if the doctor's letter was crucial, all the work you did with Curve before wasn't wasted at all!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Talochard",
                    "T": "Is that really true...? Well... I don't know."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Talochard",
                    "T": "Curve... The question you're leaving behind, I may never understand it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Talochard",
                    "T": "Anyway, thank you... and I know what we should do next — catch that awful scoundrel Jenck!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Talochard",
                    "T": "Absolutely! Definitely! He must be tried for his crimes!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "And just like that, you and Talochard return to the Court of Fontaine and start hunting for the dastardly Jenck.\\nSurprisingly, despite several days of intense investigation, you turn up no leads.\\nIt seemed like Jenck had vanished. No one had seen him, nor had any negative news regarding The Steambird surfaced...\\nUp until one day, Editor-in-Chief Euphrasie sends you a message requesting to meet in the city..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
